
Slideshow app build and install
====================================
Package with 'play dist' in play-slideshow/
Copy slide-app/dist/slide-app-1.0-SNAPSHOT.zip to your machine
Unzip
cd slide-app-1.0-SNAPSHOT
chmod +x start
./start

Slideshow app usage
=====================================

Add page: curl --request POST --header "Content-type: application/json" http://localhost:9000/pages/add --data '{"name":"DN","duration":15,"url":"http://www.dn.se"}'
Remove page: curl --request POST --header "Content-type: application/json" http://localhost:9000/pages/remove/<page name>
List pages: curl --request GET http://localhost:9000/pages
Slideshow: http://localhost:9000/

